        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Proof. By definition, Ho(G, A) = Tor2G (Z, A) = Z ⊗G A. Applying the right exact functor g A to the exact sequence",
        "bbox": [
          0.2023529411764706,
          0.6278787878787879,
